    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 28.66,
      "end": 29.76,
      "text": "The Old Hound.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 31.58,
      "end": 37.2,
      "text": "A Hound would serve his master well for years and would run down many aquariums in his time,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 37.78,
      "end": 40.98,
      "text": "began to lose his strength and speed owing to age.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 41.76,
      "end": 47.74,
      "text": "One day, when out hunting, his master started a powerful wild bull and set the Hound at",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 47.74,
      "end": 47.92,
      "text": "him.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 48.9,
      "end": 53.56,
      "text": "The later sees the beast by the ear, but his teeth were gone and he could not retain his",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 53.56,
      "end": 55.4,
      "text": "hold, so the boar escaped.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 56.74,
      "end": 61.86,
      "text": "His master began to scold him severely, but the Hound interrupted him with these words.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-014",
      "start": 63.44,
      "end": 66.02,
      "text": "My will is as strong as ever, master.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-015",
      "start": 66.78,
      "end": 68.68,
      "text": "My body is old and feeble.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-016",
      "start": 69.88,
      "end": 75.38,
      "text": "He wants to remember me for what I have been, instead of abusing me for what I am.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-017",
      "start": 78.1,
      "end": 81.18,
      "text": "End of The Old Hound.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
